* {
margin:0;
padding:0;

}

html {
	position:relative;
	min-height:100%;
}

body {
	margin:0;
	padding:0;
	background:url("../images/bgBody.jpg") repeat;
	
}

@font-face {
    font-family: 'franchise_freebold';
    src: url('../fonts/Franchise-Free-Bold-webfont.eot');
    src: url('../fonts/Franchise-Free-Bold-webfont.eot?#iefix') format('embedded-opentype'),
         url('../fonts/Franchise-Free-Bold-webfont.woff2') format('woff2'),
         url('../fonts/Franchise-Free-Bold-webfont.woff') format('woff'),
         url('../fonts/Franchise-Free-Bold-webfont.ttf') format('truetype'),
         url('../fonts/Franchise-Free-Bold-webfont.svg#franchise_freebold') format('svg');
    font-weight: normal;
    font-style: normal;

}

@font-face {
  font-family: 'fontello';
  src: url('../font/fontello.eot?43103494');
  src: url('../font/fontello.eot?43103494#iefix') format('embedded-opentype'),
       url('../font/fontello.svg?43103494#fontello') format('svg');
  font-weight: normal;
  font-style: normal;
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'fontello';
  src: url('data:application/octet-stream;base64,') format('woff'),
       url('data:application/octet-stream;base64,') format('truetype');
}

 [class^="icon-"]:before, [class*=" icon-"]:before {
  font-family: "fontello";
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: normal;
  speak: none;
 
  display: inline-block;
  text-decoration: inherit;
  width: 1em;
  margin-right: .2em;
  text-align: center;
  /* opacity: .8; */
 
  /* For safety - reset parent styles, that can break glyph codes*/
  font-variant: normal;
  text-transform: none;
     
  /* fix buttons height, for twitter bootstrap */
  line-height: 1em;
 
  /* Animation center compensation - margins should be symmetric */
  /* remove if not needed */
  margin-left: .2em;
 
  /* you can be more comfortable with increased icons size */
  /* font-size: 120%; */
 
  /* Uncomment for 3D effect */
  /* text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(127, 127, 127, 0.3); */
}
.icon-tumblr:before { content: '\e800'; } /* '' */
.icon-twitter:before { content: '\e801'; } /* '' */
.icon-dribbble:before { content: '\e802'; } /* '' */
.icon-lastfm:before { content: '\e803'; } /* '' */
.icon-down-big:before { content: '\e804'; } /* '' */
.icon-up-big:before { content: '\e805'; } /* '' */

.wrapper {
	/*padding-bottom:150px;*/
	width:1000px;
	margin:30px auto 150px;
}

.header {
	padding:42px 31px 0 31px;
	background:url("../images/bgHeader.jpg") repeat;
	overflow:hidden;
}

.headerTop {
	margin-bottom:53px;
	overflow:hidden;
}

.header .logo {
	
	text-align:center;
	float:left;
	width:179px;
}

.header .logo a {
	font:85px/69px 'franchise_freebold';
	text-decoration:none;
	color:#6b3b25;
	display:inline-block;
	width:179;
}

.header .logo span {
	font:13px/15px '';
	display:block;
	position:relative;
}

.header .logo .hand:before {
	content:url("../images/line.png");
	position:absolute;
	left:0;
	top:-2px;
}

.header .logo .hand:after {
	content:url("../images/line.png");
	position:absolute;
	right:0;
	top:-2px;
}

.header .nav {
	float:right;
	margin-top:18px;
}

.header .nav li {
	
	margin-right:8px;
	float:left;
	list-style-type:none;
}


.header .nav li:last-child {
	margin-right:0px;
}

.header .nav li a .icon-lastfm {
	background:#a99070;
	display:block;
	padding:7px 6px;
	border-radius:6px;
}

.header .nav li a .icon-lastfm:hover {
	background:#ea3d30;
}

.header .nav li a .icon-tumblr {
	background:#846d50;
	display:block;
	padding:8px 6px;
	border-radius:6px;
}
.header .nav li a .icon-tumblr:hover {
	background:#ea3d30;
}
.header .nav li a .icon-twitter {
	background:#cec0ae;
	display:block;
	padding:8px 6px;
	border-radius:6px;
}
.header .nav li a .icon-twitter:hover {
	background:#ea3d30;
}
.header .nav li a .icon-dribbble {
	background:#bca990;
	display:block;
	padding:8px 6px;
	border-radius:6px;
}
.header .nav li a .icon-dribbble:hover {
	background:#ea3d30;
}
.header .nav li a {
	display:inline-block;
	text-decoration:none;
	color:#ffffff;
}

 ul.navBottom {
	box-shadow: 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13);
	border-top: 3px solid #f7a301;
	border-bottom: 3px solid #c78301;
	box-sizing: border-box;
	padding: 0px 0px 0px 27px;
	background: #e09402;
	float: left;
	margin: 0 auto;
	width: 1000px;
	position: absolute;
	z-index: 2;
	left: 0;
	right: 0;
	top: 175px;
}

 .navBottom:before{
	content:url("../images/leftOrange.png");
	position: absolute;
	left: -20px;
	top: -4px;
}

 .navBottom:after{
	content:url("../images/rightOrange.png");
	position: absolute;
	right: -20px;
	top: -4px;
}
 .navBottom .liHover {
	height: 59px;
    padding: 0 10px;
    font: 400 16px/16px 'Lato';
    margin-right: 9px;
    float: left;
    list-style-type: none
}

.navBottom .liHover:hover {
	background:#62493d;
}



 .navBottom li:last-child {
	margin-right:0px;
}

 .navBottom li a {
	display: inline-block;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding-top: 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #ebe6df;
}



ul.dropdown {
  
  display:none;
  position: absolute;
  left:27px;
  top: 100%;
  margin-top: .2em;
  background: #62493d;
  min-width: 17.4em;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  padding: 18px 13px;
  border-radius: 0 0 .2em .2em;
 }

ul.dropdown li {
	
    list-style-type: none;
	float: none;
	margin:-7px 0px;
	border-bottom: 1px solid #806d63;
 }

 ul.dropdown li:last-child {
	border-bottom:0px;
 }
 
 ul.dropdown li a {
		font:400 16px/30px 'Lato';
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: .5em 0em;
        display: block;
}

ul.dropdown li a:hover {
	color:#e09402;
}

.content {
	position:relative;
	opacity:0.99;
	background:#dedad3;
	padding:57px 30px 54px 30px;
	box-sizing:border-box;
	overflow:hidden;
	mih-height: 700px;
}

#owl-demo .item img{
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
	
}

	
	
.afterSlide {
	height:200px;
}

.footer {
	position:relative;
	box-sizing:border-box;
	
	width:1000px;
	height:80px;
	background:url("../images/bgfooter.png") repeat-x;
	border-top:12px solid #5a453b;
}

.clickPanel {
	

  text-align:center;
  border-bottom: 3px solid #e09402;
  padding: 0 15px;
  width:970px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
  color: #97aab0;
  /*background: #203138;*/
  
}

.btn-slide .icon-up-big {
	color:#9a7664;
	padding-top: 30px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  text-align: center;
  background: url("../images/dom.png") no-repeat;
  width: 46px;
  height: 47px;
  display: inline-block;
}

.btn-slide .icon-down-big {
	color:#9a7664;
	padding-top: 30px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  text-align: center;
  background: url("../images/dom.png") no-repeat;
  width: 46px;
  height: 47px;
  display: inline-block;
}

 .clickPanel a {
	font: inherit;
	color: inherit;
	transform:translate(0px,4px);
	display: inline-block;
	
}
.slidePanel {
	background:url("../images/bgfooter2.png") repeat;
	padding:40px 30px 68px 30px;
	box-sizing:border-box;
	height:200px;
	
}

 .slidePanel .column {
	float:left;
	overflow:hidden;
	width:300px;
	margin-right:20px;
}

 .slidePanel .column:last-child {
	margin-right:0px;
}

 .slidePanel .column ul {
	color:#d88f04;
	font: 600 18px/12px 'Lato';
}

 .slidePanel .column ul li {
	color:#e7d7ba;
	font: 400 14px 'Arvo';
    margin-top: 16px;
}

.footer p {
	text-align:center;
	padding-top:30px;
}
.footer p a{
	text-decoration:0;
	color:#e09402;
}

#panelBox {
left:0px;
overflow: hidden;
  bottom:-200px;
  position: absolute;
}
